  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>A useful app here would be django-taggit:
<a href="https://github.com/alex/django-taggit">https://github.com/alex/django-taggit</a>

There is another app that implements some templatetags for getting a list of
tags and a tagcloud:
<a href="https://github.com/feuervogel/django-taggit-templatetags">https://github.com/feuervogel/django-taggit-templatetags</a>

And this looks rather interesting as well - an app that allows you to associate
multiple keywords or regular expressions with a single Tag object:
<a href="https://github.com/frankwiles/django-taggit-suggest">https://github.com/frankwiles/django-taggit-suggest</a></pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
  <tr>
